{"tid":1805741,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"運動開始後，覺得生命好脆弱","createTime":"2019-12-31T19:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T20:11:52.000Z","uid":303052,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2312cb08c7507e7fc2fad988cd04821603213b","tid":1805741,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:28:28.000Z","msg":"之前唔會成日諗依啲嘢 都係諗住係無所事事成世<br />\n冇乜愛好 冇乜目標 冇乜人生意義<br />\n<br />\n而家成日諗自己會唔會好似周同學咁路過某地方就會意外死左 唔知屋企人會諗<br />\n會唔會發發下夢就中彈盲左 咁就成世冇得見愛嘅人<br />\n好多假如 好多如果係心入面轉緊<br />\n甚至行過都會暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(分分鐘告得入)<br />\n變左鍾意同fd影相 因為可能嗰張係最後一張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會主動約fd 同佢哋講好掛住佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾着以前會覺得好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似好中二病咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然出街都可能俾車撞<br />\n但而家會覺得因為運動出事機會率大過俾車撞..<br />\n<br />\n結論係珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能杞人憂天左但依啲時勢下 有咩事真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">0101維園見</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"491e15c00b43864c52a1ae70c31b82330df0b960","tid":1805741,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:29:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DADEhn_xM0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DADEhn_xM0&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4c91172f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DADEhn_xM0</a>"},{"pid":"40b407295f9aee8061902d631961a7ca6c08c7dc","tid":1805741,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:32:25.000Z","msg":"0101維園見"},{"pid":"bb7cd572d56e3ca1a366752ec14e716b17f4060d","tid":1805741,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:33:20.000Z","msg":"維園見"},{"pid":"8e5ffdcc89473bd11de4cde98cc803f1a14cf4d6","tid":1805741,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:47:54.000Z","msg":"而家開聲吹港獨嘅手足，我夠膽講你地唔係真係想贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed7a3f56136f6a3d97df10385f899107bf1fde6d","tid":1805741,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"眼前冇人"},{"pid":"69c1f923b057dd0fc2ac53dbddeb28a74eee3130","tid":1805741,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBjFuNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBjFuNw.jpg&h=0e1bf2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9pezeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9pezeb.jpg&h=4609a2b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1933812a7e6019fbae18526dc3b43433a70050d3","tid":1805741,"uid":303750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:59:44.000Z","msg":"以前覺得啲故事好中二<br />\n劇情好唔合理<br />\n依家覺得現實更中二更唔合理"},{"pid":"ffc0d609544850ef77472b8a3b0ca9568b0f4257","tid":1805741,"uid":318284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T20:11:52.000Z","msg":"Same here<br />\n多咗關心屋企人<br />\n雖然宜家唔記得同屋企人講遲返<br />\n屋企鎖門<br />\n我冇門入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}